{"data":[{"id":"108_1753852883.658","type":"feed","offset":108,"verb":"TOPIC_ACKNOWLEDGED_ANSWER","created_time":1753852883,"updated_time":1753852883,"target":{"id":"1904808830375789399","type":"answer","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/answers/1904808830375789399","author":{"id":"2ad1552b6ddbc9d01b2b9469eeaf2c8b","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/2ad1552b6ddbc9d01b2b9469eeaf2c8b","user_type":"people","url_token":"xian-zheng-96","name":"宪正","headline":"此身不向今生度，更向何生度此身","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7d0f5485db8537335d9a3b8cb60012ce_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":1,"followers_count":4528,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false},"created_time":1746921814,"updated_time":1746948298,"voteup_count":12,"thanks_count":0,"comment_count":0,"is_copyable":true,"question":{"id":"1903854439615402354","type":"question","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1903854439615402354","author":{"id":"901f98b9d092c316c25bdd4f3ed79bcd","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/901f98b9d092c316c25bdd4f3ed79bcd","user_type":"people","url_token":"mingbible","name":"十万个不正经","headline":"个人品牌计划：从唯一性到第一性","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9f53851a51d7052599cc90d949657591_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":1,"followers_count":2536,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false},"title":"曾国藩为什么只要钱不要江山?","created":1746694270,"answer_count":0,"follower_count":0,"comment_count":3,"bound_topic_ids":[19363],"is_following":false,"excerpt":"","relationship":{"is_author":false},"detail":"","question_type":"normal"},"thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6c6e30306d1feebfdead6341faebe793_720w.jpg?source=b6762063","excerpt":"曾国藩从一个湖南小地主变成中国大地主，你说他只要钱不要江山？ 作为地主阶级，钱也要江也要山也要了，只是不从更大的地主家而是从广大农民手中夺得。 曾国藩看清了真正的主子不是最大的地主满清皇族，而是满清皇族都要跪的列强，而众列强是他无论如何也无法抗衡的。   所以一八七O年他安抚最大的地主： “皇上登极以来，外国盛强如故，惟赖守定和议，绝无更改，用能中外相安，十年无事。此已事之成效。……以后仍当坚持一心，曲…","excerpt_new":"曾国藩从一个湖南小地主变成中国大地主，你说他只要钱不要江山？ 作为地主阶级，钱也要江也要山也要了，只是不从更大的地主家而是从广大农民手中夺得。 曾国藩看清了真正的主子不是最大的地主满清皇族，而是满清皇族都要跪的列强，而众列强是他无论如何也无法抗衡的。   所以一八七O年他安抚最大的地主： “皇上登极以来，外国盛强如故，惟赖守定和议，绝无更改，用能中外相安，十年无事。此已事之成效。……以后仍当坚持一心，曲…","preview_type":"default","preview_text":"","reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp data-pid=\"a3MfeeH-\"\u003e曾国藩从一个湖南小地主变成中国大地主，你说他只要钱不要江山？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"PsFW2Kaj\"\u003e作为地主阶级，钱也要江也要山也要了，只是不从更大的地主家而是从广大农民手中夺得。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"186PvRRF\"\u003e曾国藩看清了真正的主子不是最大的地主满清皇族，而是满清皇族都要跪的列强，而众列强是他无论如何也无法抗衡的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-28a126f85edd581cf7c5213d040afb8f_1440w.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"890\" data-rawheight=\"682\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-28a126f85edd581cf7c5213d040afb8f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-190a2acc0b0b25dbd3325fde6dcd1e33_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"890\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-28a126f85edd581cf7c5213d040afb8f_r.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"7G7U46e8\"\u003e所以一八七O年他安抚最大的地主：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"aDsJWbzK\"\u003e“皇上登极以来，外国盛强如故，惟赖守定和议，绝无更改，用能中外相安，十年无事。此已事之成效。……以后仍当坚持一心，曲全邻好，万不得已而设备，乃取以善全和局。”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"y7EbnS1E\"\u003e这话既是对同治说的，也是对自己的内心独白。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"kScEd5oG\"\u003e他心目中最好的主人是米国：“米夷质性淳厚，于中国时思效顺。”可惜米国与众列强已达成共识，觉得满清政府才是它们分割吞食中国的最佳代理人，如果看上的是他，你看老曾会不会与满清皇族掀桌子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0d268cfc248c1132867648940ad50a2b_1440w.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1024\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-0d268cfc248c1132867648940ad50a2b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a4d30cc707d0d7db7fb1764e27becb86_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1024\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0d268cfc248c1132867648940ad50a2b_r.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"GupFp6av\"\u003e这一点满清皇族上上下下里里外外都门清，对曾国藩可谓是客客气气，礼貌备至，据晚清皇家侍卫回忆：曾国藩总要安排随同悄悄将散银塞至我们的袖口里，而现银我们是从不敢收取，也不敢找他麻烦，毕竟是靠他们挽救了满洲社稷。所以，在来之前，大臣会一再叮嘱我们“有礼”。来以后，侍卫还要一路“礼迎”，要威严得不卑不亢，比对王还客气，但不能失威严，要将其当做我们最该敬重的大“奴才”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"0fbbwCEK\"\u003e奴才啊奴才！最大的奴才也是奴才，不是做满清的奴才就是做列强的奴才，即使“要了”这江山，对曾国藩又有什么区别呢？他已成功令这江山变色，把封建江山变成了半殖民地，把半壁江山拱手让另一些异族来统治。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"lMWPyTKR\"\u003e中华有幸，幸而有另一位湖南后生：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"-08x5rvc\"\u003e“帝国主义和中国封建主义相结合，把中国变为半殖民地和殖民地的过程，也就是中国人民反抗帝国主义及其走狗的过程。”\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"is_thanked":false,"is_nothelp":false,"voting":0},"is_labeled":true,"visited_count":3092,"thumbnails":["https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6c6e30306d1feebfdead6341faebe793_720w.jpg?source=b6762063","https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0fbf1f24425f70d1189835c5c812cb88_720w.jpg?source=b6762063"],"favorite_count":0,"answer_type":"normal","is_navigator":false,"navigator_vote":false,"vote_next_step":"vote"},"brief":"{\"source\": \"TS\", \"type\": \"answer\", \"id\": 1904808830375789399}","attached_info":"","action_card":false},{"id":"109_1753852883.704","type":"feed","offset":109,"verb":"TOPIC_ACKNOWLEDGED_ANSWER","created_time":1753852883,"updated_time":1753852883,"target":{"id":"1933242313108338576","type":"answer","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/answers/1933242313108338576","author":{"id":"a477d1c2470e7b13d98deafd37db7f43","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/a477d1c2470e7b13d98deafd37db7f43","user_type":"people","url_token":"lu-min-yuan-97","name":"吕旻园","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d831a91eb3a16178cdb82d9163d73612_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":0,"followers_count":5747,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false},"created_time":1753700885,"updated_time":1753701036,"voteup_count":837,"thanks_count":28,"comment_count":193,"is_copyable":true,"question":{"id":"1908415539207987490","type":"question","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1908415539207987490","author":{"id":"8b54a45dbb24c4974406be839eaf85ee","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/8b54a45dbb24c4974406be839eaf85ee","user_type":"people","url_token":"zhang-jing-tong-77-47","nam